Client sends a command to the Game to create a new Game with Player race x

Game creates new Player with Race x
Game creates new Floor, sets map from file

floorgen:
Floor randomly generates, in this order:
    Player coordinates
    stairway coordinates
    Potions (types and locations)
    Gold (amts and locations)
    Enemies (races and locations)

Client sends command to Game for player to perform action
repeats until:
 a) The Player reaches the stairway to the next floor {
     goto stairway
 b) The Player's health reaches zero {
     goto dead


stairway:
    remove all Decorators from Player
    goto floorgen
    
dead:
    Client sends input to Game to either start a new game or quit program
